polarNRZ

Polar Non-Return to Zero Line Coding Technique

Calling Sequence

[polar_out] = polarNRZ(x)

Parameters

x: Digital information signal
polar_out: polar NRZ output

Description

polarNRZ -It generates polar NRZ line coded output for the given input data x.

Examples

x =[1,1,0,0,0,1,1,0];//digital information signal
polar_out = polarNRZ(x);
plot2d2(polar_out);
disp(polar_out);


